{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "7da9b87a-cf02-46d3-86c6-f9bcff99d121", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7da9b87a-cf02-46d3-86c6-f9bcff99d121@3.pkg/1772597649322/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597649821", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7da9b87a-cf02-46d3-86c6-f9bcff99d121@3.pkg/1772597649322/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597649821"}, "identifier": "7da9b87a-cf02-46d3-86c6-f9bcff99d121", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>对于应负的责任要义无反顾地承担好，因此要增强履行责任的能力。承担责任不是根据代价与回报，有选择地履行责任，更不是遇到大事、难事时才去承担责任。因此①②符合题意，③④说法错误。选择A。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>古人云：“大事难事看担当，逆境顺境看襟度。”对于应负的责任，迎着风险也要干好，要提升担当的能力，做到敢担当、能担当、会担当、善担当。这启示我们(　　)</p>\n\n<p>①义无反顾地担当起应负的责任</p>\n\n<p>②提升自身素质，增强履行责任的能力</p>\n\n<p>③根据代价与回报，有选择地履行社会责任</p>\n\n<p>④遇到大事、难事时才要担当起应负的责任</p>\n", "title": "古人云：“大事难事看担当，逆境顺境看襟度。”对于应负的责任，迎着风险也要干好，要提升担当的能力，做到敢担当、能担当、会担当、善担当。这启示我们(　　)①义无反顾地担当起应负的责任②提升自身素质，增强履行责任的能力③根据代价与回报，有选择地履行社会责任④遇到大事、难事时才要担当起应负的责任", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7da9b87a-cf02-46d3-86c6-f9bcff99d121@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754666112660", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "